Venizelos Rejects Prospect of Greece Exiting Euro Area

-- B y   M a r i a   P e t r a k i s
-- 
2011-09-21T08:40:54Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-21/venizelos-rejects-prospect-of-greece-exiting-euro-area.html
Greek Finance Minister Evangelos
Venizelos rejected suggestions that the debt crisis will force
 Greece  to exit the euro. Speaking to lawmakers in  Athens  today,
he said: “Greece is and will always be a member of the euro
zone.”  To contact the reporter on this story:
Maria Petrakis in Athens at 
 mpetrakis@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
James Hertling at 
 jhertling@bloomberg.net  